    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <pb n="1" xml:id="p.1"/>
                <opener>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>
                            <orgName key="org.1">UNIVERSAL-EDITION</orgName>
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Wien I, <placeName key="place.9.11.6.12">Karlsplatz 6</placeName>
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                    <persName key="pers.4342">Wi.</persName>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName key="place.9.11">Wien</placeName>, <date when="1949-12-15">15.
                            Dezember 1949</date>.</dateline>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Mr.</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            <persName key="pers.3263">Arnold <hi rendition="#g">Schönberg</hi>
                            </persName>
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            <placeName key="place.15.7.3.1">116 N. Rockingham Ave.</placeName>
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            <hi rendition="#u">
                                <hi rendition="#g">Los Angeles</hi> 24, Ca.</hi>
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                </opener>
                <salute>Sehr geehrter Herr <rs type="person" key="pers.3263">Professor</rs>!</salute>
                <p>Wir erhalten eben von Dr. <persName key="pers.1675">Charles B. HUTTON</persName>
                    (European <lb/>postal adress: Boite Postale No. 39, <placeName key="place.7.1.1"
                        >Monte Carlo</placeName>, fol<g ref="#typoHyphen"/>
                    <lb break="no"/>genden Brief in <seg type="comment"><orig>Angelegenheit Ihrer
                            Manuskripte</orig><note xml:id="nisn_z4b_mcc" resp="#pkehrer"><ref
                                target="letter.17761">Universal-Edition an Arnold Schönberg, 14. November
                                1949</ref>. In der weiteren Korrespondenz mit Milton S. Koblitz
                            taucht die Frage nicht mehr auf</note>
                    </seg>:</p>
                <quote rendition="#blockquote">
                    <p>„Dear Sir: Referring to your letter of <date when="1949-11-15">November
                        <lb/>15th</date>, I am informing you that my associate in <lb/>
                        <placeName key="place.15.7">Los Angeles</placeName>, Mr. <persName key="pers.1923">Milton
                        S. Koblitz</persName>, attorney <lb/>has asked me exploit in Europe the
                    possibilities <lb/>for selling these manuscripts.</p>
                    <p>I am not in possession of them. Therefore I have <lb/>forwarded your letter to
                        <placeName key="place.15.7">Los Angeles</placeName>, asking <lb/>to write to
                    you all the details. The address <lb/>of Mr. <persName key="pers.1923">Milton S.
                        Koblitz</persName> is: Postoffice Box <lb/>No. 2416, <placeName key="place.15.7">Los Angeles</placeName> 24, California, USA.</p>
                    <p>Sincerely</p>
                    <p rendition="#r">Dr. <persName key="pers.1675">Charles B. Hutton</persName> m. p.</p>
                    <p rendition="#c">Copy is mailed to  <lb/>Mr. <persName key="pers.1923">M. S<choice>
                                <sic>-</sic>
                                <corr cert="high">.</corr>
                            </choice> Koblitz</persName>.“</p>
                </quote>
                <p>Wir verweisen nun nochmals auf unser <ref target="letter.17761">Schreiben</ref> vom <date when="1949-11-14">14.
                        <lb/>November</date> in dieser Angelegenheit und wären Ihnen sehr
                    <lb/>dankbar, wenn Sie der Sache dort nachgehen und uns <lb/>Nachricht geben
                    wollten.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Mit den besten Empfehlungen <lb/>
                        <seg rendition="#r">in vorzüglicher
                            Hochachtung</seg>
                    </salute>
                    <lb/>
                    <seg rendition="#r">
                        <orgName key="org.1">UNIVERSAL –
                        EDITION</orgName>
                    </seg>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed rendition="#r">
                        <persName key="pers.3204">Schlee</persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
